Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:05.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,A miserable romance {可哀想ね　ロマンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:08.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,A tear-jerking nuance {涙誘うニュアンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:12.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,If you turn another page of your memories, {想い出のページめくれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:15.23,Sign,,0,0,0,,Here she is - heroine of the past {追憶のヒロイン} {actually, "the heroine of the recollections" but that doesn't have a nice ring to it}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:26.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,I raise my eyes to your face - {あなたの面影　見上げて咲いている}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:30.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I'm in full bloom {unsure, maybe "it's flourishing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:34.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,A sunflower amidst the blizzard - {act. in the middle of winter}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:37.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,that would be me, my dear {真冬のひまわり　それが私なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:40.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,Always on the verge of freezing, {凍えるような気持ちでいつも}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,My feelings are out of control -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:48.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,Too stiff to even say "Do you still love me?" {「好き?」と尋くこともできず}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,My lips just keep wavering in this wind! {風に揺れていたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:58.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,A pitiful Romance {いじらしいね　ロマンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:01.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,Something that only happens in dreams: {夢のような出来事}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:05.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,Trying hard to forget, I fell even more in love {忘れるために愛したの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:07.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,with heroine of the past {追憶のヒロイン}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:12.67,Sign,,0,0,0,,Miracle that I came across now is hugging me tight {めぐりあえた奇跡　そっと抱きしめて}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:16.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,This is the story of my life, I'll do my best to protect it! {私だけの歴史　守ってゆくわ}
